        <item>
            <title>Motorola 可弯曲概念手机，或可佩戴在手腕</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/29/motorola-2/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=motorola-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/29/motorola-2/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 29 Oct 2023 03:39:56 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[lenovo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[motorola]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1201238</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">近年不少手机品牌均有推出折叠手机，似乎已形成一道风潮。Motorola 或有可能推出比折叠手机更先进的手机，推出可弯曲手机。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1201239 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-25-at-1.33.42-PM-694x384.png" alt="" width="694" height="384" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-25-at-1.33.42-PM-694x384.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-25-at-1.33.42-PM-1280x709.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-25-at-1.33.42-PM-768x425.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-25-at-1.33.42-PM-1536x850.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-25-at-1.33.42-PM.png 1546w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Motorola 可弯曲概念手机，或可佩戴在手腕</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Lenovo 创新科技大会中，Motorola 率先展出一款概念性的可弯曲手机，可在不同情境下使用。手机使用了 6.9 吋的可适应萤幕（Adaptive Display），可随著弯折角度立在桌子上，或像智能手表佩戴在手腕上。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1201240 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-25-at-1.35.16-PM-694x381.png" alt="" width="694" height="381" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-25-at-1.35.16-PM-694x381.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-25-at-1.35.16-PM-1280x702.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-25-at-1.35.16-PM-768x421.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-25-at-1.35.16-PM-1536x843.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-25-at-1.35.16-PM.png 1542w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可随著弯折角度立在桌子上</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Motorola 并不是第一个尝试手机与腕带混合概念的品牌。 2016 年，Motorola 母公司 Lenovo 展示了一款名为 Cplus 的手机，该手机具有类似的罗纹背板和可折叠萤幕，可以像智慧手表一样包裹在手腕上，但从未推出过。</p><p>图片及资料来源：<a href="https://www.slashgear.com/1429251/motorola-rollable-smartphone-concept-watch/">Slash Gear</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
